5000|$|Fra Diavolo (Italian for [...] "Devil monk") is {{the name}} given to a spicy sauce for pasta or seafood. Most {{versions}} are tomato-based and use chili peppers for spice, but the term is also used for <b>sauces</b> <b>that</b> include no tomato, or that use cayenne {{or other forms of}} pepper.|$|R
